item.title: Changing name
item.dc:creator: @lancashire lancashire
item.description:
@lancashire wrote:

Ok Called Enzo,
I know the problem.
Right…Go on to Client.java,
Ok.
And Click Ctrl + H And put pimpscape in.
And theres a think it ses replace.
Put your server name in there.
Replace all.
Save and Return back to your page with runserver and all.
Ok.
DO NOT PRESS RUN SERVER!
Go on compiler.
And compile.
Then it should sey…R to run server
Run server and walla your done!
I hoped i helped!
